{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about","content_id":"5f5a7f57-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"We keep those sentenced to prison in custody, helping them lead law-abiding and useful lives, both while they are in prison and after they are released. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<p>We work with courts, police and local councils, as well as voluntary organisations, to do this.</p>\n\n<p>We run 109 of the 123 prisons in England and Wales.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p>Within England and Wales we’re responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>managing prison and probation services</li>\n  <li>supporting effective offender management</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-04-16T17:36:27Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["5f5612b0-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef",{"title":"Jobs","url":"https://prisonandprobationjobs.gov.uk/"}],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"headers":[{"id":"responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Responsibilities"}],"organisation":"05b3ff92-52c9-4577-b08e-7514b40c98ff","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2014-04-16T19:36:27+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about","content_id":"5f5a7f57-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-04-16T17:36:27Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about","withdrawn":false}],"corporate_information_pages":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about/recruitment","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/